===Adjective===
# exceeding the usual bounds of something; [[extravagant]]; [[immoderate]]

===Usage===
"I personally consider putting a wide vibrato on a single 16th triplet note at tempo 160 '''excessive''', nay even [[stupid]]."

"Well James dear boy, what is your opinion on 64th note sweeped arpeggios in a punk rock song?"

